snippet.title: Amber Alert San Antonio TX | Missing Texas Girl Lina Sardar Khil
snippet.description:
Missing 3 Year Old Girl From Texas Lina Sardar Khil.  The search for a missing 3-year-old was intensifying Tuesday morning as police focused in on the apartment complex where she suddenly disappeared late Monday afternoon.

San Antonio Police Chief William McManus said his department was "sparing no assets, no resource, to try to find" Lina Sardar Khil, who was last seen Monday at 5 p.m. on a playground inside the apartment complex grounds in the 9400 block of Fredericksburg Road on San Antonio's northwest side.
